## Authentication
You can authenticate to the Mingle API using HMAC authencatication.

To generate your HMAC key, go to your User Profile, accessible in the top right corner of your Mingle, and navigate to the tab titled “HMAC Auth Key” where you will see the “Generate” button. Using this button will generate a new HMAC key for your use. 

This will download a CSV titled “credentials.csv” to your machine which holds your HMAC username and key.  	

![HMAC Auth Key](/images/generate_HMAC.png)

<aside class="notice">Please note that regenerating your HMAC key will invalidate your existing key.</aside>

